# HavBank Styling Conventions

Every design token already lives in `src/app.css` under `@layer components`. **Use the token, don't re-invent it.** If a pattern is missing, add it to `app.css` rather than inlining one-off Tailwind chains across pages.

## Palette (do not drift)

- **Primary / trust:** `blue-900` (light) · `blue-800` (dark) · `blue-400` for accents on dark bg. This is HavBank's navy — it is the brand.
- **Surfaces:** `white` / `gray-50` (light) · `gray-900` / `gray-800` (dark).
- **Text:** `gray-900` / `gray-600` (light) · `white` / `gray-300` (dark).
- **Alarm only:** `red-500`–`red-900` — reserved for fraud, sperring av kort, sikkerhetsvarsler. Never for marketing CTAs.
- **Sustainability / success:** `green-600`–`green-800` only on `/baerekraft` and "grønt boliglån" contexts.
- Never introduce a new hue (purple, teal, orange). Banks don't have brand rainbows.

## Required tokens

| Use case | Class |
|---|---|
| Outer page wrapper | `.page-container` |
| Hero H1 | `.page-title` + `.page-lead` for subhead |
| Section H2 | `.section-eyebrow` + `.section-title` + `.section-lead` |
| Primary CTA | `.btn-primary` |
| Secondary text link | `.btn-secondary` |
| CTA on dark/colored hero | `.btn-white` |
| Product / feature card | `.card-soft` |
| Metric / data card | `.card-elevated` |
| Navy icon tile | `.icon-box` |

## Page skeleton

```svelte
<svelte:head>
  <title>Sidenavn – HavBank</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Kort norsk beskrivelse." />
</svelte:head>

<section class="page-container py-24 sm:py-32">
  <h1 class="page-title">Sidetittel</h1>
  <p class="page-lead">Ingress på norsk bokmål.</p>
  <div class="mt-10 flex gap-x-6">
    <a href="/bli-kunde" class="btn-primary">Bli kunde</a>
    <a href="/kontakt" class="btn-secondary">Kontakt oss <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
  </div>
</section>
```

Every top-level page should include: **hero → features/products → stats or trust indicators → CTA/contact block.** Match the shape of `src/routes/+page.svelte` and `src/routes/privat/+page.svelte`.

## Icons

- Always `@iconify/svelte` with the `heroicons:*` set (matches existing pages).
- Guard with `{#if browser && Icon}` so SSR doesn't flash.
- Standard sizes: `h-5 w-5` inline, `h-8 w-8` trust row, `h-12 w-12` in `.icon-box`, `h-16 w-16` hero mark.

## Dark mode checklist for every new block

- Background: pair every `bg-*` with `dark:bg-*`.
- Text: pair every `text-gray-*` with `dark:text-gray-*` (or `white`).
- Borders/rings: pair `ring-gray-200` with `dark:ring-gray-700`.
- Never ship a component without opening it in dark mode.

## Numbers & formatting in templates

- Currency: `kr 1 234` (non-breaking space thousands, lowercase `kr`).
- Percent: `4,15 %` (comma decimal, thin space before `%`) in visible copy.
- Phone: `+47 00 00 00 00`. Demo numbers use `+00 000 00 000` as in `+page.svelte`.

## Don't

- Don't inline long utility chains that duplicate an existing `.card-soft` / `.btn-primary` / `.page-title` — refactor to the token.
- Don't add animations beyond the existing subtle hover/backdrop-blur patterns. No parallax, no scroll-jacking, no confetti.
- Don't use stock-photo-style gradient hero images; the existing blue conic blob is the only decorative gradient.
- Don't introduce component libraries beyond what `package.json` already ships.
